11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 57 O.S. 2021, Section 332.4, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 332.4. A. Upon the effective date of this act, members
15 of the Pardon and Parole Board shall be deemed regular full-time,
16 salaried employees of the Pardon and Parole Board.
17 B. The Chair of the Pardon and Parole Board shall be selected
18 by the Board. The Chair of the Pardon and Parole Board shall
19 receive Twenty-four Thousand Eight Hundred Dollars ($24,800.00) per
20 annum, payable monthly, in the following allotment:
21 1. Four Hundred Dollars ($400.00) for preparation for said
22 meeting; and
23 2. One Thousand Six Hundred Sixty-seven Dollars ($1,667.00) for
24 the regular monthly Board meeting.
